{"tid":1032293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當發現好多學生有情緒問題，政府竟然係推一校兩社工，而唔係增加輔導員","createTime":"2019-02-22T09:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T10:21:43.000Z","uid":81732,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2525717fdf0fa4931fae0d54751358a42c5fd37f","tid":1032293,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】本港學童精神健康問題近年引起社會關注，據了解，下周三公布的新一年度《財政預算案》將增撥逾3億元，於今年9月在全港公營中學推行「一校兩社工」，增加人手跟進學生個案；亦有向學生「派糖」的一次過措施。消息稱，今年會續推為2020年中學文憑試（DSE）學校考生代繳考試費，以及向合資格的基層學生每人派發2000元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190222/s00002/1550773493731/中學推一校兩社工-貧窮生獲2000元津貼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00002%2F1550773493731%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%A1%E5%85%A9%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5-%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%B22000%E5%85%83%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=015343dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190222%2Fs00002%2F1550773493731%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%A1%E5%85%A9%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5-%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%8D%B22000%E5%85%83%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC&h=ecea37be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190222/s00002/1550773493731/中學推一校兩社工-貧窮生獲2000元津貼</a>"},{"pid":"1a25cb03597992ee7cd212c6c6e59e30df793fe2","tid":1032293,"uid":81732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a50b6dcf4dd6e1a8eee9e50c19c3082795956e1","tid":1032293,"uid":77143,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"乜中學社工有用咖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a806765f94deac2988150697f47ba442905ed1a9","tid":1032293,"uid":81732,"like":12